Pumpskin::

Somewhere in a dark corner of the Predacon base, a creature's snores 
are interrupted by Hydras's shout.  "Erm, hrm, harrum, Pumpskin, 
terrorize!"  The huge gourd splits up and reconstructs itself into 
the crazed warrior's robot form.  "Heheheh, sounds like the boss is 
angry.  I wonder what it's about?"  Still yawning, the ex-Maximal 
proceeds to the appointed place.

OOC: He still hasn't thought to get rid of his Iron Squad insignia, 
even though he proved his Predacon nature in the last major battle.
